---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Learn more about the person behind Lifetime Rookie." />
		<style>
			.about-content {
				max-width: 650px;
			}

			.about-content h1 {
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			}

			.about-content p {
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
			}

			.about-content ul {
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				padding-left: 1.5rem;
			}

			.about-content li {
				margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<article class="about-content">
				<h1>About Me</h1>
				
				<p>
					Hey there! I'm the person behind Lifetime Rookie. I believe in staying curious 
					and approaching life with a beginner's mindset, no matter how much experience 
					I gain along the way.
				</p>

				<p>
					This blog is where I share my thoughts on:
				</p>

				<ul>
					<li><strong>Life</strong> - lessons learned, reflections, and personal growth</li>
					<li><strong>Soccer</strong> - the beautiful game and everything around it</li>
					<li><strong>Wealth & Money</strong> - building financial literacy and independence</li>
				</ul>

				<p>
					Whether it's a quick observation or a deep dive, I write to think and share 
					what I'm learning. Always a student, forever curious.
				</p>

				<p>
					Thanks for stopping by!
				</p>
			</article>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
